{"tid":606000,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[平反大革命] 为什么要笑 00 后写简化字喎…?","createTime":"2018-03-26T06:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T06:24:05.000Z","uid":132968,"like":166,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0b696553c29c8c555364b8c5031d17ebba1f503b","tid":606000,"uid":132968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:56:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蠢人</span></span>就緊係寫<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蠢字</span></span>架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Stupid 00's</span></span> writing <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Stupidified Chinese</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n殘體字係係 1960s 中共發明俾班大陸文盲提高識字率先用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSo, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">00's = 大陸文盲</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n宜家就算連大陸一線城市都開始轉返做正體字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/26/145137_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F26%2F145137_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=d4e3b10e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反觀，我哋班天才 00 後宜家先開始轉殘體 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係唔讚下佢哋都唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b34d9f7ac53bfbc5f2bc73882ea5c4c313f4fc","tid":606000,"uid":21423,"like":13,"dislike":26,"score":-13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:57:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09d2157650ee393998399ae96b3d013a264fecf5","tid":606000,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:59:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8e24b65ac8949c4cea7c12790c617e1b91afdc","tid":606000,"uid":134779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T07:01:08.000Z","msg":"banter jai講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5c0a8616556f43e4fcda454d3907a2cdcac47f","tid":606000,"uid":152520,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T07:10:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/api/res/1.2/vOuo1llNUbqyvW_UueQzDQ--~B/YXBwaWQ9eWlzZWFyY2g7Zmk9Zml0O2dlPTAwNjYwMDtncz0wMEEzMDA7aD00MDA7dz02MDA-/http://images.takungpao.com/2016/1122/20161122114234623.jpeg.cf.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Flo%2Fapi%2Fre